  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 425°f (220°c).",
    "trim the broccoli and cut it into florets.",
    "toss the broccoli with olive oil, garlic, salt, and pepper on a baking sheet.",
    "roast the broccoli in the oven for 20 minutes.",
    "add the potatoes and carrots to the baking sheet and continue roasting for another 20 minutes.",
    "squeeze some lemon juice over the broccoli and toss with chili flakes if using.",
    "garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot.",
    "check the potatoes and carrots for tenderness and adjust the cooking time as needed."
